transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, Joanna speaking, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes ma'am, my name is Danilo Paoli.

Speaker 1: I would like to just clarify that my previous order was only a one-time transaction,

Speaker 2: Why are they charging my PayPal?

Speaker 1: Okay, let me pull up your account, can I get your name and date of birth?

Speaker 2: I did not ask for a refill, but along the line there's a charge in my PayPal.

Speaker 1: Okay sir, can I get your name and date of birth?

Speaker 2: $413.

Speaker 1: Can I get your name and date of birth?

Speaker 2: My name is Danilo, my name is Danilo Paoli, October 19, 1954.

Speaker 1: Okay, thank you, I have your account here, I do see that you are a VIP status customer,

Speaker 2: And how did it work out with the Viagra 100 milligram which you received?

Speaker 1: Were you happy with the results?

Speaker 2: The previous time we had a problem, I ordered the AGB, they just gave me a regular Viagra,

Speaker 1: That's why I told them to replace it.

Speaker 2: Then along the line I told them this is a one-time transaction.

Speaker 1: Okay, did you have an opportunity to try the AGB that we sent you?

Speaker 2: No, I didn't take it because it never worked, that's why I didn't order anymore.

Speaker 1: Now I was surprised, there's another charge on my card, on my PayPal account.

Speaker 2: Okay, but you haven't tried the AGB that we sent you?

Speaker 1: Yeah, it never worked.

Speaker 2: So, because I know we sent you the generic first, and so you're saying that the AGB that we sent you didn't work for you either?

Speaker 1: No, it's the same thing, the same thing that they sent to me.

Speaker 2: I guess what?

Speaker 1: I know they look the same, but they are actually different.

Speaker 2: No, let me clarify, I want you guys to stop charging my PayPal.

Speaker 1: Okay, that's not a problem, sir.

Speaker 2: I didn't ask for a reason.

Speaker 1: As a VIP status customer, you have the option to set up your account however you want.

Speaker 2: You're not locked into any monthly fees or a monthly subscription.

Speaker 1: We're not a subscription.

Speaker 2: We are a telehealth, so you actually can set up your account however you want.

Speaker 1: You can modify the frequency and quantity of your orders.

Speaker 2: You can also put a pause on your account for up to six months at any time.

Speaker 1: That way, if you wish to place a future refill order with us, you'll have access to it.

Speaker 2: No, no, I want you guys to stop charging my PayPal.

Speaker 1: This is a one-time transaction only, before I mention it again.

Speaker 2: Why do I have to charge again?

Speaker 1: I want you guys to refund that money to my PayPal.

Speaker 2: Okay, I'll go ahead and do that, sir, and you will be canceled.

Speaker 1: You will not be able to order with us again.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I want you guys to refund my money to my account.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: I didn't ask for a refill.

Speaker 1: Okay, I understood.

Speaker 2: I've gone ahead and issued a refund for that and canceled your account,

Speaker 1: and you will not be able to order any Viagra with us again in the future.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I stopped that on my PayPal also.

Speaker 1: Are you guys going to return that money to my account?

Speaker 2: Yes, it can take up to five business days.

Speaker 1: Okay, what's your name again, ma'am?

Speaker 2: Juliana.

Speaker 1: Juliana. Thank you very much, Juliana.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you, sir. Have a good day.

Speaker 1: You too. Bye-bye.
